# TypeScript

## Single import path

```ts
import type { Profile, Vehicle, UserRole, Infraction } from "@/types";
```

Do not re-export or duplicate enum literals (`"driver" | "agent"`) in feature files.

## Schema workflow

1. Edit `src/db/schema.ts` (Drizzle)
2. `npm run db:generate` or hand-write `supabase/migrations/*.sql`
3. Update `src/lib/types/database.ts` (`Database` + enums)
4. Add row aliases to `src/types/index.ts` if new tables

## Naming

| Layer | Convention |
|-------|--------------|
| DB columns | snake_case |
| React components | PascalCase |
| Functions / hooks | camelCase (`useStaffDocuments`) |
| Query keys | camelCase namespaces in `queryKeys` |

## API return types

Define fetcher return types next to the fetcher in `lib/api/` or export from `@/types` when shared across hooks and components.
